      "date": "2016-11-09 17:20:19.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nHi Elena,\n\nThe test output showed that:\n\n -----============= acceptance-small: ha ============----- Tue Oct 11 12:24:03 UTC 2016\n Running: bash /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/ha.sh\n /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/ha.sh: 12:24:04 1476188644: -c is mandatory\n /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/ha.sh: 12:24:04 1476188644: Usage: /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/ha.sh -c HOST[,...] -s HOST[,...] -v HOST[,...] [-d DIRECTORY] [-u SECONDS]\n\nThe ha.sh was not written with the Lustre test framework, so it has not been supported by autotest system yet.",
